\caption{Reconstruction error distribution for Experiment 1.}
\end{figure}

Experiment 2 validated the effectiveness of the consistency gate. Cosine similarity computed across multiple noise scales successfully separated clean samples from those with potential triggers. This is illustrated by the clear separation in similarity measures, as shown below:

