\caption{Cosine similarity measures for the consistency gate in Experiment 2.}
\end{figure}

Experiment 3 compared the full iterative refinement pipeline of DTCBS with the base method. Loss curves indicated that DTCBS achieved a lower reconstruction loss over successive epochs, and the evolution of flagged sample counts demonstrated a progressive reduction in suspect data:

